OL,4,CGentleman' get training from military
OL,6,FJonny Blair goes to meet the actors
OL,7,Fbeing put through their paces by the
OL,8,Fmilitary.
OL,10,FA number of actors performing at a
OL,11,FNewcastle Theatre have been put
OL,12,Fthrough their paces with the military,
OL,13,Fto get into character for their latest
OL,14,Froles.
OL,16,FStars of the musical 'An Officer and a
OL,17,FGentlemen,' which is currently at
OL,18,FNewcastle's Theatre Royal, went to
OL,19,FFenham Army barracks to get some
OL,20,Fpractical training for the military
OL,21,Fthemed musical.
