OL,3,CActors from the show 'An Officer and a
OL,4,CGentleman' get training from military
OL,6,FIt is based on the award winning movie
OL,7,Ffeaturing Richard Gere as an aspiring
OL,8,Fnaval officer who finds love. The 80s
OL,9,Fsoundtrack is still listened to today.
OL,11,FGiving the orders throughout the day
OL,12,Fwere army reservists based at the site
OL,13,Foff Barrack Road in Newcastle.
