OL,4,CGentleman' get training from military
OL,6,FGeorgia Lennon is from Hartlepool and
OL,7,Fplays Paula.
OL,9,FShe said: "It's very special. This is
OL,10,Fthe closest I'll get to my home town
OL,11,Fof Hartlepool. This is a theatre I
OL,12,Fgrew up watching so much live theatre
OL,13,Fin and to now be on the flip side of
OL,14,Fwhere I was as a little kid watching
OL,15,Fthat stage, it feels so special."
